Behavioral Design Patterns wo patterns hote hain jo objects ke beech communication
aur responsibility distribution ko define karte hain.
Objects aapas me kaise interact karte hain.

Core Idea
Creational → banana
Structural → jodna
Behavioral → chalana (behavior control)

Main Behavioral Patterns (11 types)
1. Observer = Ek object change hota hai → sabko notify
2. Strategy = Multiple algorithms, runtime pe choose karo
3. Command = Request ko object bana do , Action ko encapsulate karta hai
4. Chain of Responsibility = Har handler decide karega handle kare ya pass kare
5. State = Object ka behavior state pe depend karta hai
6. Template Method = Algorithm ka skeleton define karo” Steps fix, implementation vary
7. Iterator = Collection traverse karna”
8. Mediator = Sab mediator ke through baat kare
9. Memento = State save & restore
10. Visitor = Operation add karo without changing class
11. Interpreter =  Language/grammar interpret karna